thread.title: Amber
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Amber

author: Amber
title: Amber
text: I always receive quality stamps from Rubber Stamp Champ. I used them for my small business first - they had the best prices! After that I ended up ordering a personal stamp for return addresses on some invitations and thank you notes. I moved - order a new one. I used them on my Christmas cards this year and so many people asked where I'd gotten it. Definitely recommend them.
